WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:03.937 --> 00:00:09.109
How many roads must
a man walk down

00:00:09.109 --> 00:00:12.946
Before you call him a man?

00:00:14.748 --> 00:00:19.753
How many seas must
a white dove sail

00:00:19.753 --> 00:00:23.289
Before she sleeps in the sand?

00:00:24.724 --> 00:00:30.497
Yes, 'n' how many times
must the cannon balls fly

00:00:30.497 --> 00:00:34.334
Before they're forever banned?

00:00:35.735 --> 00:00:40.540
The answer, my friend,
is blowin' in the wind

00:00:41.174 --> 00:00:44.577
The answer is
blowin' in the wind

00:00:55.922 --> 00:01:01.761
Yes, 'n' how many years
can a mountain exist

00:01:01.761 --> 00:01:05.298
Before it's washed to the sea?

00:01:06.666 --> 00:01:12.338
Yes, 'n' how many years
can some people exist

00:01:12.338 --> 00:01:15.875
Before they're allowed
to be free?

00:01:17.377 --> 00:01:22.882
Yes, 'n' how many times
can a man turn his head

00:01:22.882 --> 00:01:26.586
And pretend that he just
doesn't see?

00:01:28.455 --> 00:01:33.860
The answer, my friend,
is blowin' in the wind

00:01:33.860 --> 00:01:37.664
The answer is
blowin' in the wind

00:01:48.475 --> 00:01:54.414
Yes, 'n' how many times
must a man look up

00:01:54.414 --> 00:01:58.384
Before he can see the sky?

00:01:59.519 --> 00:02:05.458
Yes, 'n' how many ears
must one man have

00:02:05.458 --> 00:02:09.195
Before he can hear people cry?

00:02:10.530 --> 00:02:16.102
Yes, 'n' how many deaths
will it take till he knows

00:02:16.102 --> 00:02:19.372
That too many people have died?

00:02:21.608 --> 00:02:27.013
The answer, my friend,
is blowin' in the wind

00:02:27.013 --> 00:02:31.017
The answer is
blowin' in the wind

